{"type": "article", "id": 6752, "title": "Manolo 多功能储物架", "description": "", "date": "2015-02-25T07:19:02Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 11, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605234227R9aNHMiOl7kYptQU.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;-webkit-text-stroke-color:#000000;-webkit-text-stroke-width:initial;\">\r\n\t来自意大利的设计师 Ilario Branca 最近为意大利家居设计品牌 Formabilio 设计了一款多功能储物架 Manolo，在一个大型木质搁板与两个小尺寸搁板上共配置了 64 个圆状把手，并配有两只衣架。整体设计简洁且灵活，方便用户可以根据自己的实际需求组合成不同的布局。Manolo 可以扮演衣架、储物架等多种角色，提供正方形与长方形两种款式，棕、白、黄以及绿 4 种颜色。定价 358 欧元（约合人民币 2536 元），<a href=\"https://www.formabilio.com/shop/home-accessories/shelves/manolo-shelving-system\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;-webkit-text-stroke-color:#000000;-webkit-text-stroke-width:initial;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234224bYqC7JVBtclIvU3y.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56601467\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234225ZEL5iuvQtFqfVpC0.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606052342259C7QWO6pNbTPVlX3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56601467\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234225spd4NElORUt9PfJa.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56601467\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234226zxknPtcbJyC4VM2f.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56601467\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}